interesting points: The observation date was November 1, 1953, and the report was received on November 4, 1953, via telephone., The object was described as disk-shaped and hovering above the lake., Flashing lights were observed on the object at the time of observation., The report was part of Project Blue Book, which involved analyzing UFO sightings., There are mentions of declassified protocols regarding the documentation of UFOs.

location: Big Moose Lake, New York, USA
